{
  "stem": "12810.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother cooking something what was my favorite, and bring it to me in the afternoon-- but she can't come in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She just give me in the fence a little bit of soup and things to-- to have a little bit of home cooking to her little girl.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then one day, she come and said to me, I heard they take us away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said oh, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now what-- what they want with the old women and the old mens, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because no young people was anymore in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but if I say to her that time to go somewhere, maybe she's still alive, and I never forgive myself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to her, no, Mommy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You just go home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing will happen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never see her anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back to the-- back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They take her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next morning, 6 o'clock, they take her away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How do I know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my father give some money of that man who was in-- working in the same place where I was working.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he bring me the news.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Non-Jewish, non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the [NON-ENGLISH], you know, to--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Brick factory to-- to ready to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's why I was escaping, because I want to go after her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] We was ready to the wagon in the factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They come to us in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, put your things together, because you're going somewhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then they cut our hair shorter to have it-- you can see everybody can see it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They are a Jewish girls, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then it was a shorter, I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, I have the star always in my working blouse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I put it on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we're going in a line.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
